# Graphical Description of Immunogenicity Data {#immuno-graphical}

## Pairs plots

```{r immuno-graphical-setup, echo = FALSE, message = FALSE}
library(here)
library(latex2exp)
library(knitr)
here::i_am("immuno_graphical/report.Rmd")

## define study name
study_name <- "mock"
```

```{r, fig.cap = "(Mock data) Pairs plots of D1 Ab markers: baseline negative vaccine + placebo arms"}
include_graphics(here(
  "immuno_graphical", "figs",
  paste0(
    "pairs_baselineMarkers_BaselineNeg_",
    study_name, ".png"
  )
))
```
